{
  "number": 3828,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/3828",
  "title": "Upgrade preact-compat",
  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe 🙏**\r\nThis is by no means urgent, but integrating instantsearch into a project using Preact X (e.g. 10.0.0-beta.1) causes issues during page load (see https://github.com/preactjs/preact/issues/1655)\r\n\r\nSo just raising a potential issue that might arise more often as and when Preact X is released and more Algolia consumers upgrade. And I expect it will be taken up quickly given it adds support for latest React 16 features (hooks, context)\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like 🤔**\r\nMove to new `preact/compat` instead of `preact-compat` (perhaps when X is stable)\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered ✨**\r\nOur interim solution was to alias `preact-compat` to `preact/compat`\r\n",
